public class Tests extends Object
The Tests class specifies a set of tests implemented using the JUnit tool. These tests use Mooshak test files as input and generate the expected result of running these tests as output. The class is implemented for testing the Paintball project. To use this class you need to include the JUnit 4 library in your runtime environment.
